# HISTORY

# #) This test should have been run with the flag "-u 3".
# #) A SpinBox with 2 Text children will appear on your screen. One will
#    be STRING and one NUMERIC.
#    The item displayed in the STRING child should be "B".
# #) The item displayed in the NUMERIC child should be 0.03.

CompareVisual TextF1 
CompareVisual TextF2 

# #) The two arrows should be at either end of the Text widgets.
#    The down arrow should be sensitive.

CompareVisual SpinBox3

# #) Set focus to the STRING child. Both the decrement (left) arrow and the
# increment (right) arrow should be sensitive.

LocatePointer TextF1
ClickMB Btn1
CompareVisual SpinBox3

# #) Set focus to the NUMERIC child. Both the decrement (left) arrow and the
# increment (right) arrow should be sensitive.

LocatePointer TextF2
ClickMB Btn1
CompareVisual SpinBox3

# #) No warnings should appear on the term window, indicating uninstalled
#    or incorrect resource converters.

# C)
Continue

# E)
Exit
